    "### What to Look for in the Results\n",
    "\n",
    "The Deep Q-Network should demonstrate:\n",
    "- **Learning Progress**: Gradual improvement in policy performance over episodes\n",
    "- **Policy Convergence**: Stabilization of Q-values and decision consistency\n",
    "- **Exploration-Exploitation Balance**: Proper ε-greedy behavior during training\n",
    "- **Reward Maximization**: Increasing cumulative rewards over time\n",
    "- **Generalization**: Ability to handle unseen container configurations"
   ]
